<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('./partials/head') %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden">
      <div class="bg-[#F7F9FF] pb-18">
        <%- include('./partials/main_nav_bar') %>
         <div class="px-6  md:px-10 py-6">
        <div class="pt-16 pb-12 lg:pt-32 lg:pb-4">


            <h2 class="ruby text-2xl font-semibold h-fit leading-[130%] text-clip md:text-4xl lg:leading-[120%] lg:text-6xl">
                <span class="mb-2 text-base font-normal block lg:inline-block lg:mb-0 lg:mr-16 "> 
                  <li> 
                  Qui sommes-nous
                  </li> 
                 </span>
                Nous vous assitons pour trouver ce qu’il vous faut en quelques clics
                </h2> 
          
          <div class="flex justify-end mt-4 lg:mt-8">
            <div class="text-gray-500 md:max-w-[75%] lg:max-w-[50%]">
               Chaque projet immobilier est unique. C'est pourquoi nous vous assistons dans vos recherches.Il vous suffit de nous indiquer vos critères essentiels : type de bien, budget, localisation, et plus encore.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
       
      </div>
       
      </div>
      <div class="px-10 py-16 lg:py-20">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-18 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-y-6">
          <div class="col-span-1 flex flex-col h-fit lg:flex-row">
             <p class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-8 text-2xl md:text-4xl">Décrivez votre recherche:</p>
            
          </div>
         
          <form class="col-span-1">
           
            <div class="border-b-[1.5px] border-gray-200 pb-12">
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-600 mb-4">Type de bien recherché</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-black rounded-lg">
                  <span>Appartement meublé</span>
                </div>
                <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-black rounded-lg">
                  <span>Terrain</span>
                </div>
                <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-black rounded-lg">
                  <span>Location d'habitation</span>
                </div>
                <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-black rounded-lg">
                  <span>Terrain agricole?</span>
                </div>
                <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-black rounded-lg">
                  <span>Web App</span>
                </div>
                <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-black rounded-lg">
                  <span>Hosting & maintenance</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-b-[1.5px] border-gray-200 py-10">
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-600 mb-2">Zone géographique recherché</p>
              <input
                type="text"
                name="name"
                id="name"
                placeholder="Email address"
                class="bg-transparent w-full focus:outline-none"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="border-b-[1.5px] border-gray-200 py-10">
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-600 mb-2">Votre budget</p>
              <input
                type="text"
                name="name"
                id="name"
                placeholder="Email address"
                class="bg-transparent w-full focus:outline-none"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="border-b-[1.5px] border-gray-200 py-10 pb-4">
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-600 mb-2">Description de votre recherche</p>
              
              <textarea name="" id="" rows="3" class="bg-transparent w-full focus:outline-none"></textarea>
               
            </div>
            <div class="border-b-[1.5px] border-gray-200 py-10">
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-600 mb-2">Votre nom?</p>
              <input
                type="text"
                name="name"
                id="name"
                placeholder="Full name"
                class="bg-transparent w-full focus:outline-none"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="border-b-[1.5px] border-gray-200 py-10">
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-600 mb-2">Votre numero de téléphone</p>
              <input
                type="text"
                name="name"
                id="name"
                placeholder="Email address"
                class="bg-transparent w-full focus:outline-none"
              />
            </div>

      
            <div class="py-5">
               <button type="submit"  class="px-6 py-4 bg-[var(--cg-accent-green)] hover:bg-opacity-75 text-white rounded-xl">
                                  Soumettre
                                </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
